quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,45,"Bahe urugero rw’ubuzima bwo ku isi ko ari nk’amazi twamanuye mu kirere, akuhira ibimera byo ku isi (bigatohagira), ariko nyuma bikumagara, bigatumurwa n’umuyaga. Kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  18,46,Umutungo n’urubyaro ni imitako y’ubuzima bwo ku isi (buzarangira). Naho ibikorwa byiza bihoraho ni byo bitanga ingororano n’amizero meza kwa Nyagasani wawe
  18,47,"Unabibutse umunsi tuzakuraho imisozi, ukabona isi ishashe hose hagaragara, maze tukabakoranya bose nta n’umwe dusize"
  18,48,"Bazanagezwa imbere ya Nyagasani wawe bari ku mirongo (babwirwe bati) \"Rwose muje mudusanga (mumeze) nk’uko twabaremye bwa mbere, nyamara mwaribwiraga ko tutazasohoza isezerano (ryo kubazura no kubabarurira)"
  18,49,"Kandi buri wese azahabwa igitabo (cy’ibikorwa bye), maze ubone inkozi z’ibibi zitewe ubwoba (n’ibibi) bigikubiyemo,nuko zivuge ziti \"Mbega ukorama kwacu! Iki gitabo ni bwoko ki kidasiga (icyaha) gito n’ikinini kitakibaruye!\" Bazanasanga ibyo bakoze byose birimo, kandi Nyagasani wawe ntaweajya arenganya"